div.p: School Board Meetings: During the virus shutdown, all Board meetings will be conducted by Zoom video conferencing and are OPEN TO THE PUBLIC. As with any board meeting, the public can listen and watch. If anyone wishes to speak, click "Unmute" on your screen, and the host will, if it is at an appropriate point in the Board's discussion, unmute you.
